quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  27,67,"Ke kaloku abo bangakholwayo bathi: “Ingaba xa sele siluthuli kunye nookhokho bethu, siza kubuyiswa (sikhutshwe emangcwabeni)"
  27,68,"Sathenjiswa ngako oku, thina nookhokho bethu ngaphambili. Oku akunto yimbi ngaphandle kokuba ziintsomi zabantu bakudala"
  27,69,"Yithi kubo: “Tyhutyha-tyhutyhani ilizwe, nibone okokuba saba njani na isiphelo sezaphula-mthetho.”"
  27,70,Musa ukukhathazeka ngabo okanye ube buhlungu ngoko bakuqulunqayo
  27,71,"Kananjalo bathi: “Inini na (inzaliseko) yesi sithembiso, ukuba nithetha inyaniso?”"
  27,72,"Yithi wena: “Mhlawumbi sele ikufuphi emva kwenu inxalenye yoko ningenamonde ngako.”"
  27,73,Inene iNkosi yenu Izele buBubele ngabantu kodwa uninzi lwabo abanambulelo.”
  27,74,Kananjalo iNkosi yenu Iyakwazi oko kufihlwe zizifuba zenu noko zikuvezayo
  27,75,Yaye akukho nto ifihlakeleyo ezulwini nasemhlabeni koko iseNcwadini ecacileyo
  27,76,Inene le ‘Kur’ân ibalisela aBantwana bakwaSirayeli okuninzi koko baphikisana ngako
  27,77,Inene yona isisiKhokelo nenceba kumakholwa
  27,78,"Inene iNkosi yenu Iza kugweba phakathi kwabo ngogwebo lwaYo. Yona nguSobunganga, uSolwazi"
  27,79,Ngoko ke thembela ngoAllâh; inene wena usenyanisweni ecacileyo
  27,80,"Inene wena akungekhe wenze abafileyo beve, ungekhe wenze izithulu ziluve ubizo xa sele zibuye umva zijibilikile"
  27,81,"Yaye akungekhe ukhokele iimfama uzikhuphe ekulahlekeni kwazo. Uya kwenza kuve kuphela abo bakholwayo kwiiVesi zeThu, abo ke ngamaMuslim"
  27,82,"Kananjalo xa iLizwi (elingummiselo) liwile phezu kwabo, Siya kuzisa kubo isilo sivela emhlabeni sithethe nabo, kuba abantu abazanga bakholwe ngokunyanisekileyo kwiiVesi zeThu"